---
// Evolutionary Conservation section
---
<section class="px-6 py-16 border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-neutral-400">进化保守性</h2>
      <span class="px-1.5 py-0.5 text-[10px] rounded bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 font-semibold">NEW</span>
    </div>
    <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm mb-6">
      E1659在所有受测哺乳动物中100%保守，横跨约8000万年的进化历史。
      周围基序PEIFTEIGTIAAG在每个物种中完全相同。
    </p>
    <div class="bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 rounded-lg overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="w-full min-w-[500px] text-xs">
        <thead>
          <tr class="border-b border-white/5">
            <th class="text-left px-4 py-2 text-neutral-400">物种</th>
            <th class="text-left px-4 py-2 text-neutral-400">位置</th>
            <th class="text-left px-4 py-2 text-neutral-400">残基</th>
            <th class="text-left px-4 py-2 text-neutral-400">序列环境</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr class="border-b border-white/5 bg-red-500/5"><td class="px-4 py-2 font-medium">人</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-neutral-400">1659</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-red-400 font-bold">E</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-neutral-500">PEIFT<span class="text-red-400 font-bold">E</span>IGTIAAG</td></tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-white/5"><td class="px-4 py-2">小鼠</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-neutral-400">1693</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-green-400">E</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-neutral-500">PEIFT<span class="text-green-400">E</span>IGTIAAG</td></tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-white/5"><td class="px-4 py-2">大鼠</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-neutral-400">1693</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-green-400">E</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-neutral-500">PEIFT<span class="text-green-400">E</span>IGTIAAG</td></tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-white/5"><td class="px-4 py-2">牛</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-neutral-400">1647</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-green-400">E</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-neutral-500">PEIFT<span class="text-green-400">E</span>IGTIAAG</td></tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-white/5"><td class="px-4 py-2">绿猴</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-neutral-400">1659</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-green-400">E</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-neutral-500">PEIFT<span class="text-green-400">E</span>IGTIAAG</td></tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-white/5"><td class="px-4 py-2">猪</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-neutral-400">1650</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-green-400">E</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-neutral-500">PEIFT<span class="text-green-400">E</span>IGTIAAG</td></tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-white/5"><td class="px-4 py-2">狗</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-neutral-400">1649</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-green-400">E</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-neutral-500">PEIFT<span class="text-green-400">E</span>IGTIAAG</td></tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-white/5"><td class="px-4 py-2">蝙蝠</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-neutral-400">1646</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-green-400">E</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-neutral-500">PEIFT<span class="text-green-400">E</span>IGTIAAG</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-4 py-2">熊</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-neutral-400">1643</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-green-400">E</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-neutral-500">PEIFT<span class="text-green-400">E</span>IGTIAAG</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 mt-3">
      9/9个物种在该位点均保留谷氨酸（E）。周围13个残基的基序在所有受测哺乳动物中完全相同，横跨约8000万年的进化历史。
      如此高度的保守性强烈提示该位点具有重要功能，支持任何替换均具有致病性（按ACMG标准属PP1支持证据）。
      数据来源：UniProt直系同源序列，基于基序的比对。
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
